divs: Sighting Detailsim not sure what i saw, or if this qualifies as a ufo or a satellite, but on the date specified i was at a local starbucks with my boyfriend when i looked up at the sky, it was clear, no stars, you couldnt see the moon. as i watched i saw an object coming up slowly from the south it was a greyish metallic object, it was dull, not shiny! and it just seemed to glide really slowly across the sky going north! i dont understand if that was a satellite or not, but it was clear, it was round and perhaps at the height of a police helicopter at most. i couldnt hear any particular sound as the street traffic was louder
